ef=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111243)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111243)\">2 Ne. 25:14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111306\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111306)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111306)\">2 Ne. 29:14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115830\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115830)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115830)\">D&amp;C 121:38<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116597\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116597)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116597)\">D&amp;C 136:36<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106465\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106465)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106465)\">2 Kgs. 1:10-14<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107722\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107722)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107722)\">Mal. 3:1<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107751\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107751)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107751)\">Mal. 4:5-6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115640\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115640)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115640)\">D&amp;C 110:13-16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">19. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108153\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108153)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108153)\">Matt. 22:4<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"1